    <item>
      <title>南非非国大启动联盟谈判，称拉马福萨将继续执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-s-anc-starts-alliance-talks-says-ramaphosa-to-stay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党非洲人国民大会自 1994 年种族隔离制度结束后在纳尔逊·曼德拉领导下掌权以来，一直占据议会多数席位，但该党目前已开始与竞争对手进行组建政府的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-s-anc-starts-alliance-talks-says-ramaphosa-to-stay</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 11:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票后，破坏者雅各布·祖马掌握着南非的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-elections-jacob-zuma-has-south-africa-s-fate-in-his-hands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅各布·祖马在被执政党非洲人国民大会赶下台之前，曾领导南非近九年，但饱受丑闻困扰。如今，他可能在南非的政治前途中扮演重要角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-elections-jacob-zuma-has-south-africa-s-fate-in-his-hands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 10:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
