    <item>
      <title>中美防务战略冲突成为新加坡论坛关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/conflicting-us-china-defense-strategies-dominate-singapore-forum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末，齐聚新加坡的全球防务领导人面临着对该地区相互矛盾的看法：美国主张扩大印度-太平洋地区的军事演习和伙伴关系，而中国则批评“外部势力”干涉和平与稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/conflicting-us-china-defense-strategies-dominate-singapore-forum</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
